> Client Calls are not cancelled after a call timeout
> ---------------------------------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-255
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-255
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: Bug
>          Components: ipc
>    Affects Versions: 0.2.1
