> DFS client should try to re-new lease if it gets a lease expiration exception when it adds a block to a file
> ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-563
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-563
>             Project: Hadoop
