> Enhance streaming to use the new caching feature
> ------------------------------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-576
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-576
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: Improvement
>          Components: contrib/streaming
